                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831029-50-off267 t17831029-50-cd268"></join> last, one piece of another of pearl, value 6 d. three guineas, value 3 l. 3 s. one crown piece, value 5 s. and one copper halfpenny, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831029-50-victim760" type="victimName">
